PRODUCTION USE NOTICE: This project uses pre-release dependencies, including
Microsoft.Extensions.AI.Agents (1.0.0-rc4) which is a release candidate and
may contain breaking changes. Before deploying to production:

- Pin all dependency versions and test thoroughly
- Review Azure OpenAI usage limits and costs
- Evaluate security implications of AI-generated content
- Ensure compliance with your organization's policies on AI tooling
- The maintainers assume no liability for production incidents
